    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237190/extras/6734349fa29a683954f5840aa4953929.poster.avif?t=1728305853\" width=618 height=185 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237190/extras/6734349fa29a683954f5840aa4953929.webm?t=1728305853\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>Sami is busy celebrating his birthday party, when suddenly, the evil Albert VII appears in the sky riding his new airship and kidnaps all of Sami's friends! Rumors say that Albert VII plans to open a zoo on the moon... Could he be plotting to add Sami's friends to the exhibit?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Help Sami free his friends one by one as you visit all kinds of exciting and wondrous locations and get ready to run, jump, rail grind and, most of all, roll your way to victory! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237190/extras/a8ba244603e07c155b649c401881afde.poster.avif?t=1728305853\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237190/extras/a8ba244603e07c155b649c401881afde.webm?t=1728305853\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237190/extras/a8ba244603e07c155b649c401881afde.mp4?t=1728305853\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237190/extras/98abd86f9bc4fdd34913cfa37333e691.poster.avif?t=1728305853\" width=618 height=185 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237190/extras/98abd86f9bc4fdd34913cfa37333e691.webm?t=1728305853\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>This DEMO contains the following:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Five fun levels</strong> lasting between 30-40 minutes of gameplay in total</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lots of collectibles!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>Sami</strong> <strong>as a playable character</strong> (more characters will be playable in the final game)  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>New accessibility options</strong>, allowing you to choose how you want to play</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Three languages: <strong>English</strong>, <strong>Spanish</strong> and <strong>Japanese</strong> (more in the final game)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >New and exhilarating songs by <strong>returning composer Evader Music</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237190/extras/ac2968ec7d54e92835f0b3a9119ec8c5.poster.avif?t=1728305853\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237190/extras/ac2968ec7d54e92835f0b3a9119ec8c5.webm?t=1728305853\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237190/extras/ac2968ec7d54e92835f0b3a9119ec8c5.mp4?t=1728305853\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Super Sami Roll is not your standard 3D platformer series, these are rolling-physics based platformers! Movement is free-form and expressive, allowing for unique playstyles and precise control as you navigate your way through each of the challenging levels on offer. Keep your momentum up by using Sami’s tongue to grapple and jump over dangerous obstacles and enemies, and sometimes even skip entire areas! <br><br>It's up to you to create your own path. Do you want to take it slow and enjoy the beautiful scenery, or do you want to discover all of the skips and tricks to be the fastest lizard possible?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Once again, it's time to ROLL!</p>",
